<style>
   @font-face {
       font-family: 'SF UI Text Regular';
       src: font_url('http://104.236.142.210:8080/assets/SanFranciscoUI/sf-ui-text-regular-webfont.eot');
       src: font_url('http://104.236.142.210:8080/assets/SanFranciscoUI/sf-ui-text-regular-webfont.eot?#iefix') format('embedded-opentype'),
            font_url('http://104.236.142.210:8080/assets/SanFranciscoUI/sf-ui-text-regular-webfont.woff2') format('woff2'),
            font_url('http://104.236.142.210:8080/assets/SanFranciscoUI/sf-ui-text-regular-webfont.woff') format('woff'),
            font_url('http://104.236.142.210:8080/assets/SanFranciscoUI/sf-ui-text-regular-webfont.ttf') format('truetype'),
            font_url('http://104.236.142.210:8080/assets/SanFranciscoUI/sf-ui-text-regular-webfont.svg#sf_ui_textregular') format('svg');
       font-weight: normal;
       font-style: normal;
   }

   html, body {
      display: table;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
   }

   * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'TimesNewRomanPS';
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #000;
   }

   a {
      text-decoration: none !important;
   }

   .mailer-wrapper .mailer-top{
      text-align: center;
      color:#fff;
      background:url('<%= Rails.application.secrets.localhost_name %>assets/healthcare-top-bg.png') 100% 100% no-repeat;
      background-position: center 0px;
   }

   .mailer-wrapper .string-top-container{
       margin-left: -22px;
      height: 165px;
   }

   .mailer-wrapper .string-top{
      position:absolute;
      width: 800px;
      height:50px;
      top: 109px;
      background-color:#41b6a6;
   }

   .mailer-wrapper .string {
      text-align: center;
   }

   .mailer-wrapper .string-top .image-center{
      width: 160px;
       height: 50px;
       margin: 0 auto;
       background-image: url('http://104.236.156.197:8080/assets/rectangle-2.png');
       background-repeat: no-repeat;
       background-size: cover;
   }

   .mailer-wrapper .string-top .image-center img {
      height: 50px;
   }

   .mailer-wrapper .string .string-top-container img {
      margin-top: 15px;
      height: 135px;
   }

   .mailer-wrapper {
      padding: 50px 100px;
   }

   .mailer-container {
      width: 800px;
      height: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      border: 1px solid #979797;
      border-radius: 16px;
   }

   .mailer-content .title,
   .mailer-content .title-signature-primary,
   .mailer-content .title-signature-secondary {
      font-weight: 600;
   }

   .mailer-content .title-signature-primary {
      margin-top: 55px;
   }

   .mailer-content .title-signature-secondary {
      margin-top: 20px;
   }

   .mailer-welcome .title-signature-secondary {
      margin-bottom: 48px;
   }

   .mailer-confirmation .title-signature-secondary {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
   }

   .mailer-content .signature {
      position: absolute;
      margin-left: 10px;
   }

   .mailer-confirmation .mailer-content {
      padding: 100px 30px 100px 60px;
   }

   .mailer-welcome .mailer-content {
      padding: 145px 30px 100px 60px;
   }

   .mailer-confirmation .signature {
       top: 474px;
   }

   .mailer-welcome .signature {
      top: 637px;
   }

   .mailer-content .button {
      border-radius: 3px;
      background-color: #41b6a6;
      color: #fff;
      font-family: 'SF UI Text Regular';
      font-size: 16px;
      padding: 12px 40px;
      display: inline-block;
   }

   .mailer-content .button-verify {
      margin-top: 40px;
      margin-bottom: 115px;
   }

   .mailer-content .controls {
      width:100%;
      text-align: center;
   }

   .mailer-content .title {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
   }
   .mailer-confirmation p:last-child a {
      text-decoration: underline !important;
      color: blue !important;
   }
</style>
<div class="mailer-wrapper mailer-confirmation">
  <div class="mailer-container">
   <div class="mailer-top">
      <div class="string">
          <div class="string-top">
             <div class="image-center">
               <img src="http://dev.ehr1medical.com:8080/assets/ehr.svg" style="width:232px;height:88px;" alt="EHR1 Logo" />
             </div>
          </div>
          <div class="string-top-container">
             <img src="http://104.236.156.197:8080/assets/num-top.svg" style="width: 146px; height:248px;" alt="EHR1 One Num Logo" />
          </div>
      </div>
   </div>
   <div class="mailer-content">
   <p class="title">Welcome, <%= @resource.provider.try(:title) %> <%= @resource.provider.try(:last_name) %></p>
      <p>Literally ethical Odd Future, VHS tattooed taxidermy Wes Anderson mumblecore keytar Truffaut jean shorts. Listicle umami keytar Schlitz quinoa Vice DIY mustache aesthetic cornhole. Mustache four loko stumptown taxidermy, bitters cardigan heirloom Wes Anderson Shoreditch aesthetic. Hoodie Pitchfork cardigan deep v, American Apparel gentrify skateboard wolf. Selvage banjo sartorial, vegan Pitchfork taxidermy messenger bag Intelligentsia plaid viral whatever High Life flexitarian irony. Twee PBR plaid beard cronut, vegan banjo brunch PBR&amp;B messenger bag pickled. Bicycle rights distillery biodiesel leggings vinyl Helvetica.</p>
      <p class="title-signature-secondary">Sincerely,</p>
      <img class="signature" src="http://104.236.156.197:8080/assets/mailer-signature.png" />
      <p class="title-signature-primary">Andrew J. Smith</p>
      <div class="controls">
        <%= link_to 'Verify Now', confirmation_url(@resource, confirmation_token: @token), class: "button button-verify" %>
      </div>
      <p>If you canot see the button above, please click or copy and paste
        the following link into your web browser:
        <!-- link_to 'http://{url}/{authentication-token}', confirmation_url(@resource, confirmation_token: @token) -->
        <%= link_to "#{Rails.application.secrets.localhost_name @resource.confirmation_token}", confirmation_url(@resource, confirmation_token: @token) %>
      </p>
   </div>
   </div>
</div>
